HfxXdKrs8cKridrWH1dyV4x1vsX7bYOzX-cbHX9trEhXxKQrqfQC8Jf8bJwNXO6qALHsQXvalllMcihOY-RSNe312Ev4az4g4NzOfX3INwhkpp_zpRujOOg3Q/7FbIUBsYlyqvr0kC8Z_E1wuUlvPCyZXG/7" title="在溃败中"&gt;因为昨天在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的关税冲击的后面，一场溃败&lt;/a&gt;从美国股票中撤出了约2.5万亿美元。现在，投资者正在辩论外国人，尤其是中国，是否可以对全球税款&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/5rzZU8Nbltw7MFpxq5zDDGUJjxgjGYSHF9XqsjnGnKIcfgjFdV-r23w-bRB0J-PPxjRSsKDyUDKpRB-Tad9EeDDESpHg1fxn5lCZoL1ADmffRx8Dzb4t6bB0R9pl4yVArx8mEeBjP8c4Ug0fWit7mXFCL1y7YAuoF49eNMW38m7avkoGH884yKTYx7ZOJCqESpSEn-iQrrvR_h8z44oIGCZJch7jL7E4-WtLxtgKOrpr86dnJTgXmgSjj4BU3_beFhkI5G8utvlf5rTNBRr6ES6Tw0D6ebj_eZwAbV42rTwzFERkSPAD6_GmsgijrJFrbYrcPfZRvJgcjwt2Z9cIaKAyY-xoOLNGKKFQtnyx0XPiN8yywCYIMQZ_zAk/3t3bez_rruJpQxXwSRRgpJZV_NjFhhdW/7" title="向后扩展"&gt;进行&lt;/a&gt;报复。万斯&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/Vtq1XhfEjCNPBtVyVOlzRlc2ejFVyGuYkW88g-c2gvlZaVkRbbKMqPqnK1n2x7YINXAc531EEugElnpp-FJMsv1OMnR9V24lwCQiAhpF5Qx3mdI9INQTqRjlo4nO08BZXSA83XKWqd-86xB1oUJAPocmuvOxHCTf7nWKJIy3S6iJUhPp-41CPggNOPoplKgFU4h8vNhQe_9MT49MWFrJQAqOonzwNJyO8EEaq23M21erKI0IqAJXDk9U4WI3NbaO8_DRrA9k_uX6z8cOwr96zdKCiOBhRgLJqfEntzbF6b2GEbz97BIxRaTKI--jRBj98sWlazrlJ4-zwL5VU47kw09LhIoGgERXvCGVyglwLgsFsiyd0HHP6ZyEEpg/slAaVPi22HaRwFjA0CI40XsqzB93I-kR/7" title="淡化了市场的行动"&gt;淡化了市场的转变，&lt;/a&gt;因为临时痛苦的爆炸。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; &lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;法国总统伊曼纽尔·马克龙（Emmanuel Macron）敦促全球最大的贸易集团欧洲联盟的企业&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/nTt76Wu8iyMjgH1Mt8MjGAqwgvIU8U7RtvIlxwv0gEMvOS8KITgc-CQemlCMsXmAIEiLzwS2AVgYuGJgpgZpAtQqd8gJ-CqGcClGhdLjwXcMH2zslxYMhypH48NGqoGgnJ2V6KZyjGM9MmjUw2aOIPwUV05xb9dIAooNYIbbGtLpe-V4uKrjgFF6AciArX8uwV70AQKwyVLFpMbWkiJpfg0B8Ep1KaLnDv7B5yo33yo9zm3tikEWq0-MO6twZ1Vk3Yxh-yArgTcsDDkG9NVryDAB_6Ih3LfYqnV6iBST5GVjLe1vZq-MxwKJqpJS-e9DfIsp4bCBl927sVc3_-L1l9A2x6GSH1c1VHF9UL8-fkRI6QdAmBBQfvn4