ng&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/Oy-EOuEeqU9Qb0CFO8MTmpjxerAwy6Eco9SH1wfDa5orXFz8G4vu0PQ2c7qwIQjLB7gzFVUH4MBqP2mENPM5pWr2qeTLQp5kB7piwd6Lk_G_PcRbNa892JbN4hkvXBzpVx36aBRmVGEtKFC86j4_NMk5GAHcVDinA7FlYejvKEH-Vbi-OAMZ1c0n3IjZG8Emye54_JqxeQihH6zfLnMDoPwx58Y--iECq9UZwgGnRwbE2Vv1RKHZ9L8fxdRh3WtXsMZXC8TO2bp4ryWTKE6QfBsTuHu1klmCDkZd1KeccglVixcT6Wx0NERvghH32R4hFpBFms-JHmcoYCzmigp7RQ21vMM9GbP0Gwut6qhfVXdS3rzzJZq7_brkwns/ChKfJYa97uSJpmgBp1bN0oCbN7ZSxRdT/7"&gt;在12月的&lt;/a&gt;短暂戒严宣言中将总统Yoon Suk Yeol撤职，为总统竞选铺平了道路，以结束已经抓住全国数月的领导层面的真空。宪法法院&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/FgPkwox_-RjhKJCuopsugG-uwpmUiX-rJaYsNRuONcZ8pJw2L3PoV__uRUza-TYk5nLmNhFjNHEpXA1I3T1G_kueMRulsTtbvhYlDs1GlHxGOLH8kRKLIFy0PIQOx2GKmSZn1bTVJ6kXwPfe_Yp07wO3i6nWP3IM6_oDJ39gdLug9VkyUenOoQ2wXQuCAZ-y2eB3e0x5ptrhMejjvz-pZRDHnjmrZoYFk2AzdpMKHo3WahCo9L5LvgHs_qCPzdzBks64u6ROiDdY4GvUYSghVUje-7aw7DgYiAW2fkhq8bcKQk7QkZTkQYUA4eEs8O3ilAuaTdloZsS8AHd35Sd8ehlVTrMvSRG_Jp-u1DdZtqJ2ox2w611hFT8veNI/TVL2JiNNVt1OaYP78veOt013Yai2T1T_/7"&gt;今天的一致裁决&lt;/a&gt;将在60天内举行举行，与主要反对派民主党的领导人李·詹·穆恩（Lee Jae-Myung） &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/fKts0buNV_N5l6MbQZ_c41gqmyWGbsGfE6eX6cuAhmh9ik8WoGAQJ5yi6Hopzp1x0O464XMqPK_8gaEJGZBhKov-DTgfsyZoRTAqGm0Io49uxHMTp0ZllfNB1jnAzfe2iNcdaZkrvajci0GNcjUdB-5iybo1MwGYk5GDPbby4FMIMlqIF8zBVj19Dh2yuf10wWzD9HrfVmnPHDITrrruKc4Tl1K74uvKeCmQGQduWgtITtBMLGbmQ0inJ5s432HMBTg-_M2wEE6XO8UxFEvE7Ek7tr7MaFKFc_djP8kX5go9o0w2DhkjppLk6b0J8B8jyEYpc6VsmBB4V1dCali-esqz_5abagmL1VFejNlxJJM6pvT3roRKHmV_g3c/vDouIQX0AszHWxdC4yQuQNo_0UmnN1V4/7"&gt;在民意测验中领导&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;在特朗普对弗拉基米尔·普京（Vladimir Putin）总统感到沮丧之后&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;，美国特别特使史蒂夫·维特科夫（Steve Witkoff）和俄罗斯&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;谈判代表基里尔·德米耶夫（Kirill Dmitriev）在华盛顿举行了两天的会谈，因为他对俄罗斯对乌克兰战争的停火&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/8lemZNrW6LUuUnBuD8zgmry_0dgygP2-ZqHB2suGB0kWbR0At3wFW_fyQaWJ_YZDt5WR8-Nftq1TtiWjk1EQQsU0yZhBnXGAFBMuq7F9NCKPNL044eoH9a23WeUcMiNz2LD0j2KEYXNlSjpNGgMBD5K6K5yGvjxoi5KQwUhczv-VzkhpU3Ix6_rOt1yzOVyeepJMExuRwDwxql9LitZK0Tgudly_Z9-3lD-ppbFUxe5vQ8PZC18PdkU6H3suHr15p2lyYjThdkjNMqzr0Nz4ZQVz7PFfgqDcYJXDr0qVTtlG72BAeR-9H-CKghnvuQ2If_HjgGpI1KeQh294yahdGHOklXohgN0Obp-K1jfCbxW9iu-WuSfBwKutgWo/SFxbLRg8CeGMgdbjOX94GZCzQA01Tqjt/7" title="缺乏动力"&gt;缺乏势头&lt;/a&gt;。消息人士说，美国现在正在等待德米特里耶夫（Dmitriev）向普京&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/4hCwgoeRu7K2WXvdoaPAhAw779zAe6Z0FJLrIEFd-dsGdOkG72UAdvbiOb1zlsWki1Bz2AqpzYvZcstebaPHqEi_UM9okai6H6vrqOrhPSvWmiusTFHFPKmMlyy3L4l8OEknh7tVBitxGkhO_2Kn5qsZLRRkD0BVZpKdrEkm7befukjn1GGfhrikZeKY9X6U2ST-puUACQ-sbA5APfYs5feiai-Medq2V7yqsBOtCYXtz5_GYg1L9q8nPEOotonRgLGNrTaU02a-nW8SGDhNIwse-UV5_bGuPo5kuyA1Zh6itLhfiWTrVA6xMwtNi-9U4XBHWZySDOOvujx37a7cmQUjpsXg49z-QrN0mhXT7JoP6xsLiGFWhZcf-n8/T0Iv0ddxjMYJNEnlSSo6K-fPr6YZkHfO/7"&gt;报告&lt;/a&gt;，然后双方以任何下一步的步骤向前迈进。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; &lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;Hakainde Hichilema在2021年赢得了赞比亚总统大选后，在Graft使非洲国家衰弱并从国际资本市场中驱逐出去后，他承诺将打击&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;腐败。四年来，一系列政治事件以及对以前财政部官僚主义的惠斯利布尔的待遇表明，Hichilema可能不会&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/529gxawYbgOMMxGGfH2N4mThRGtsqSDIHvB7DtcpFeFGyATr_kcRkHxvoIK6hCk6oXfxUtueJVD4KVtai7c00lm-sIPlejLHzJhDCLuWNWN0MgENJhYQqo-MhU1wwKxc3Cem9q7ViBR3-kMjBzV2buxMTCtskVXlPyHoExSuFNQ-yEweKGKIi_-yo0adSvOY3kj42Ut53jaexi1eoylt5myDzwMsSB8lSKe2rMwvWPI-PJXrOF7c-9JmpPNpgHxjdqUZj9tfb6YHEiFsuWqcfg40fKsdQYLwymU3D7Xx-X35bN_ylrMUN1chVDkttOKbGYAsFWLmQwUJFohWpAc6_Tn4ZJp2p0yRcTIswHVchSKaICXBtPkuJZDHlBI/lcVM_dQfhOvXBHUQNh928ghADBQZ2aeg/7"&gt;完全破坏&lt;/a&gt;最近的过去。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;丹麦的顶级外交官在特朗普&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/K46D2MFUGuXss1pltjrCCGyBj55wimWVxzNk2HC2Iq8i2yaPsDxKc5vfNU7_1MQ1RFK8O59ZtGI7-oHo1pakIAB9fWxGzsf5YneUEJ5x_v_8HHCkZgLwWnkHdqX_YxiF9H1Nu293tKjQ2jMJPQ6-92yhcuCq1O-vZLZY7QWDZS9db_tk5baBSdO0lu1R5qPsSU4q8-aw6Bl1ZbRFygVzq-oQNEtkgOO_C9mI3LanLKj6l6pTfybrz4O-Q0W-zIXzvv4tjWQa-W1dQ512jsftJVoZaqCwbgV4pA8l3V0vqf5xxr_iIqhfjWFJXbLMUZaMpWss5sV03oXWbyx0b9izScF9aNWLcLYd9HC5F_s-L7k3iyLFd5rJDCa1UBI/SlZzaeQDGcqFzhJIM5u8-r6BY8XTxls-/7"&gt;对格陵兰的侵犯&lt;/a&gt;方面&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;站起来&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;，有效地结束了他们希望的安静外交政策，他们希望这一问题消失。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ie.AU4ckAri8/v0/-1x-1.jpg" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ie.AU4ckAri8/v0/-1x-1.jpg" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 130%; margin-top: 8px;"&gt;丹麦总理梅特·弗雷德里克森（Mette Frederiksen）周三在努克（Nuuk）。&lt;i&gt;摄影师：朱丽叶·帕维（Juliette Pavy）/彭博（Bloomberg）&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; &lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;以色列已将士兵送&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;入加沙北部的部分地区，称其想扩大对阵哈马斯的行动，在那里&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/uRciwHT6E-zGkW6yyEuy9z3FaAlgEGtBZ-0Ia6-X2llLDtXT5MageVzrc6WXsZmIzyWm_99PBpVpeGJTWYpvF6aJZhFST_JlrE-aCRaA4qyH1fTz1vDMma0_haSBedEzmpe2aiu8MWRV6uHgillSp0JDfJxiLrkO1hkUnQa81Vk2-eFBHV1M7ac_VuLWbYhrKZCzUMXcTbGdQrYcQZ3OVi7FT4XVtsUVTJR1zJ-WCB3aQyjck4qs-ctC7uqPZeSuh0_AlDB7jJAi_NoGLcxySp2dzolQynfMNiVM8u_UWqSACbKufAgNy8GNq-eCMhn3JBSHXRDjn9bQPFIy2xSMPlV341nEG971mMRKQ9vu8aMmAMOlXqfA0mT