ks.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/rPd03cAbyRzUwAjp6X0Fu6IyzK6yyHRjMqqpBOaUEQPUNtEcRc-BpXRZiDdvyLn5jHtOf_pEA_vw5bSjVXWEwPZytBW8KTUG3Z3hRpfejdAvZe4u0KAv8VLa9ipFwYG9aUcbbARedUDFcyBPugDMcSlwphh2sCQDfIbqiIRIl1HwBWFKtzu_n_Ro-9xCR0X8j4qX56PNdiVBFlMYw2ViCfMBpCadD8u47l8zyVfsSlMa-RaSXCy5nkgaVobyLtaUK43FqrCoN2PyMnzeGaFfXl75lvz3VVtEMlnK_XgRdZCgp7xFEOaD4T0zZeMrpyi3hMLBj51WcLwLN5d_hvSswi4fokmciNxRArFQJTp8D6XKSyLIArhD6U_uGok/W4azScnAOGvskzDrpoHZAaeEFblY_E9P/7" target="_blank" title="关联"&gt;新税级&lt;/a&gt;称重，以抵消拟议的税收立法的某些费用，这与数十年的共和党政策背道而驰。谈判的新最高利率为39％至40％，高于目前的37％。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;击中所有角落&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;昨天的股票市场抛售向房屋敲响了唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）认真对待全球贸易体系的信息 - 至少目前，人们&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/x8ngyJJdAvH01DgK357hWUIUXFPmtztT7eqX4LpDalqqr7ABnHtLBXp_6x2roftA0cWUk_OMCoXiC8p3nUFivm_BkJUCZ-nN5rTKoAn5Jvpv9hO_z2tMPKP8jxYIUIHx5cBXO6mJ9wDPTTRFOnOFx2QNuISHUAcJTtpVxb0jQ9vVBdWxbQyq7PpvvE5KPwlHurlYj4lKxixAwO1VR4fseKY_vzCd_ZXkUSTilDGV_MtV-8PR-WLNESD66jYzDxTsIdGFnP0ZGL48BJkvtX3sJBFVwhlJgTC88jZYg1gVsmxOD4BChOQeicImL1-OcV7Y_dWaR8XMvLEBtbHm_EbfWuXqegG_a7krGTt8ePjw-wb3IbmYUixP_aCkHZQ/k2kQB5egJEQ6lLX_X7rs5R3DKvLSuL3Y/7" target="_blank" title="关联"&gt;对市场崩溃的恐惧&lt;/a&gt;并不会阻止他。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;这次&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/28giihUqvHch4pORXhxYIFQQ_ODyX3q4oXkcVDEtvjbg3bkhyQHlwSe2WBe4KhRz4Q8ZXIdT8U0r4RIW0C5_qDdRzHPUp_ds79D-k1DESJPqcCrA6NRevP4fL055pVBii_BsfQFXdch2c4i4n9498uLbmfs5lRVA-M-MiZZOpGAWTwku0nBHzcj7gzo9NVET4kLiGGph_b_RAWPUWhiX8QtziWTUnOlNu5SvjMlP-kDFYdVWXuJlhQkBrAn8IVHaQXfxJ6YJdqXwXJPUA3Lxq9Ob99WcZfgRA8bzxg_9bkiGuQidt1H0b5CU7IAZBb74liiQBlugnanQq2DAw7cIFVoBCiBB4rY0EOuN8I6jtQtauq_FCsiu0gg-Vj0/AT0iipfGvs-5GEaY2ZO5xCNF3JlTZJTK/7" target="_blank"&gt;暴跌袭击了市场的各个角落&lt;/a&gt;，甚至没有直接受到关税影响的部门，因为人们担心贸易体系触发的经济衰退被吓到交易者。财务是一个很好的例子：KBW银行指数索引了其自2023年3月的地区银行危机以来&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/fWu_kAIDQwuDW9KAIdNnxO23-VT1gaYLVzbyCeKa6NuF9_UL0YybsEutTFf6SFlG_hZ991y2dQOykgDvl4KFvGUJekpmzYtN1G_O4lv9muQo5Y5klXbxqglNOwTa_PAa2zPSa3cPYFP82hHTDkpIbFrbsLGGHgannuoCd9XSOL26i2DFHnjzylCpktO_LPSl7gdKVpW69YXB9DkIxwlXxSZlNjZBzodIH2W502bYcq7wL90qQj4RjVai2KxA4RO95moPDUlN2hij44g2tHvoNOiYCM3T6jjjMV6Lrw8O8lSW2sRgLfj-i4ew9aQzTFs9RMA5BlJfs2JY2PBsriYU5KX2ydf5SLZMUU8MCKtkBy799YEXdCChRMyCrz4/6La4X0mmZtZCZVBYDcbdRNQK9HBlDZrC/7" title="Citi，美国银行以来，自区域银行危机以来，最糟糕的溃败"&gt;最大的滑坡&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;另一个潜在的衰退信号：昨天被视为经济领先地的运输库存进入熊市。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iQ7TgvWAMyk4/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iQ7TgvWAMyk4/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;公司债券也被殴打，美国垃圾债券以自2020年以来带来了&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/g1kiyPAKRdUk1Ku4gpbDeFDuZE8RNfTqaTVKLO6RXj-0w2Ce_NIOs7i1xSsLJz79eXbCGLu7aIj8b9Qz8Ur5euywDnf1doylppijE-fBqquFZwLXonWtkbWl3tXs9pFlHy1nO1Wv60OZ1TFJbsgpUA2Xeim_kfau_lDSUneWjUVfFPMUBOmHx1zxTb_EBh3rHhKTy-otGs7fCa0SQww6ZoABVNm1824NHl4AyO9RDC2QU_n0DrohgMtN8b0yNGH1DdyaEwkHLr_HsrGcaGCLzVftSCR8kiYLbsCEX-qJT7JO3NSZKdZfx5x6h4FzEGYDf-Xw1IGaOV1fRZ_JeFbYZjoS4ZxY0iDphbibmRbdsoj2XbFK0a95t1xywvc/O_pYERTEpCd__POdqbwYaQqaewcXpvOe/7" target="_blank" title="关联"&gt;全球高收益债务最大的低迷&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;这一切都为美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔（Jerome Powell）提出了赌注，后者已经面临着平衡美国在通货膨胀再次激增的风险的艰巨任务。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;随着特朗普政府在埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）的总督团队的指导下削减成千上万的联邦工作，而迅速地担心失业率可能会增加，这也是如此。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; Brandywine Global Investment Management的投资组合经理Tracy Chen说：“关税对我们和全球增长确实不利，但也增加了通货膨胀的风险。” “我认为美联储现在无法以所有这些不确定性削减。”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;华尔街的反应很快：瑞银全球财富管理&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/EiolwlDWcrdWtRDZHMcC2rPKjWZct3RqvR3rj5O6wis0W4sSLpZICo5YuihOnSa_fpM-F8BT5uW4HRGd58-nl2lllzQexzwppcAa7f1cRJApCgJ36qRWh134XXXFG5Teqeb5eydSlVVr5sIZHnTh4fZUz5TGX4yIFEnUi7l3ArGUGm387wDzxXAdfTZkXZQJzb3RWEZyHyPBJe4lSu0DY9dDr2tIY7KauYyGTf6W_uUzR2T0506oEzfsVkZrcK-Laa_Rv83YL4sUvNarcvsc4NkWCZKpmrnEaTJA1VzP8Em7X2KDi1IXfYIF4Mf9TOssvFOjNPvrfV44RPs-pr1nfQ_2MhoWZremffCvpcBADtH7ZOPwOEspcH5GaWI/KREcuNNZ8CLLz8BQBdHN3jWzQcsK4Nby/7" target="_blank" title="关联"&gt;降低了美国的股票&lt;/a&gt;，由于较低的收入估算和估值，其年终500年的年终目标从6,400削减到5,800。新的预测仍然意味着从昨天的结束中获得了7.5％的收益。 - &lt;em&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/W6cKxBBOg4WlhHWpKUNwR32UO_ZDZIg39X1mTZ1uXfF4V1YFffLmtZ-WRW6mHLxfV2RdbXmvt52RI54k-kdtuD-VIMzvo5SRxtkHJ0NE3thpkuTSAKCmm-KVy2hKTL-Yb5ZPUXDZf1021uDu-TP2HGWo-iNCjM65AmWVu5mqFo9C20krKh1cSqU8leI87x6mVolNLoFJ8YuPwydQgSuM9Kj2BwekELUucxZ3EekuDyTofS1c1ofMEkGTplQSGO0_CrRB12Yhxc2-Yd_53oR011NPzFGHKHbnyo3Fkq_KZAzkiHl_vZBhwztGE7YSUa-WC68iZmHYX7d0Ys1na4dbSeWMc4N6ywWkybUbpfZwpT3FtVcHSkCs9nX2ADY/jytO8UEzxi5qOkGozpmfo_LZhbobaKm4/7" target="_blank" title="关联"&gt;利兹·卡波·麦考密克（Liz Capo&lt;/a&gt; McCormick）， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/q1wcerd1moDVpp1tzXkmyt1kYHlYIWbUJ00n6Z-JgnCJfdw9dajxJBzZi3y4NphgaTO0vpI4P0ZpdLQ6Efq7Kgw5RTJGMmcgPqMDMfaMBBnv5bYbwsTOUlNI4qhYT0ao_oeXjwUY0p67mAdJbcqbz32ERo7Yebv0oa1xe0-JJiLTwBKt4eZZn1awYkTgU8xpFkhgNY_wZKBlXCVNkMci_0E9t9tOyU63__uWmeILpW7l5q2Rb4BqFTJSDpP3fEWgAAeQKt9M6zihBygcsUteEkro8VzKab9j0RnVDZcD96uzDPfNjwiLlPExUe47uq91WAyKwB3LT7OH3GE4TIQHF4IDUsajtGyT9mV7ZkqPikisgtZmRvYXbSELNT8/-NRmBcAsSWvL8h8IBoYrdXPhPqcG6SsL/7" target="_blank" title="关联"&gt;卡门·雷涅克（Carmen&lt;/a&gt; Reinicke）， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/hpJhr-LJ439-akriysZCD5AnZvCoU5if-nsPNk3C8EPHm1voSBHLtRTTqTwqMMFtTxfVwXZZrAkdCbcH9fIqqGUrONu9nq0m-ZoHo7noer7ORxsGGWPeCSFJDii7VwEoaf0I7Jmy_1qRI-HjPkPr1c5T3ssgqhwrRbe9klV0aDnzPoR3qNQw5gIgBTIsabQLQZhVFbuIH0OgLgfc72aGF7RLw6rHRy94YzWNVEugevRldp9wF6Wfu34yCu9Q5o6Df3FfxWVEEfWeHlSDFu5BOQa9gSfO0kmza-zzb6XqkBY7dDrjK8FtCFEFwmJ--qxYmXZnTgPyYr_xK-wEDWnufG_7GBooyoa84u4FHskFVvRSk1aDGibeigwP1IM/U1IN_a-FRqOw-EGp2KqERJI2UhdajLZo/7" target="_blank" title="关联"&gt;朱利安（Julien Ponthus）&lt;/a&gt;和&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/pnk_DJ7s8FT9MoJ2YLGMdedf3eGVQE45hych3WJGynW5Zr12FB6vUy9gUi0SNyJApgyvtb5pxBtSIotYCJJHQatYd3rDCkG1ZAlrkClXZijO-DtR4Y7anlFDozFpQv9Q2UY0bOAvRkbGA29IxrEyIN7QV9xSacywn57sdRiEQxCkuToe-hrdti3GJWTUilUOvDDc-tSiuAI6O7X8A1QKZbUy-t9cj9_4cRpOtfoaU3ezuUXEed_fK35Pt-zscmD2Q5wfkMeDUbLAMrCQtgskecporAJZL5PPyx0eQ3jMABjfGu0a4cQyApDIAyVF4m9Ouqd-vm256UcnU-UU4dov38n73pbxzKQ18D1FKUGv9M3AX4_opYHg_RpyVuc/S6Rg0QI6FZ6s9ZSvXbRi1cg-6Pvh72J_/7" target="_blank" title="关联"&gt;Esha Dey&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/em&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="auto"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td align="center" colspan="2" style="padding: 0 0px;" valign="top"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/By3PPP1mHKARGRMKCwgybrpLWirDv_na_Q6