由于关税&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/si7P8763D-Xyjv4nPWPtoNUjXK8wmpNc2SrEnl1_amx_IxsE3xODr-xTjHgIgoNiozA84XgjTtizGsgFYkuI2PqAa4HnuKJmbShzRwMYcCyoEEzuzuhoNlnZE_0PC3eokmR7Ppx3oW6ZvSWbvYce2Ja-CldhJ_rw-gh8R2SyC2yh06ws83LrW4uLpDlb7YCePOls3RXRSgFnNZeSPQoX5pa2MVU6MS7B77TrY_BFyvsFT2dNa_rziXQ5JFCDlhBd9eS690RqghsHvagPtNyC6QzTXPYK_sfb3Jd7Bngfdd259JEfNMfEnZRMPx_g9DqunPQNFuIubP_L6Y9s0C4HJZAwjsvDkXp4oQBZs_atIQDqapB5MbjVPb5hvlM/NPm0npwegiLLqtWEwAEg2CzIAroL8hCz/7" title="华尔街交易台，曾经是一个世纪的关税冲击震惊"&gt;损害了&lt;/a&gt;科技股，该公司的市值昨天关闭了2万亿美元。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iVFtaWRlz6K4/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iVFtaWRlz6K4/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ul style="padding-left: 10px; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;特斯拉&lt;/strong&gt;股票下跌0.5％。 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/_H_GunNmpRMe1Awsuuxom8N0rm0CWBvXzx_ZqMp-OXORRhp0UdUmIp7ddIEHrZPiobRpWiFfrthjEcjBFmxHulz1g0wAvq4OA7q-VWgVmYTPTpNtCbuDMxJokHhTXdbjyXrgOEcKT7I_gStv2Nz-v4SU5qm4O-RgnyQG45n23bZA0trqtph0WuYra9mRkrep-DpO8BcrZDsC2JvEG4NwDbJP6H5isfkyLKzK2D11_IaGS0Rk9GF0MP_Fmyd0a0wBGYarvaEPuZICPpWIhpo9OK4ABsJR5PdiW7TC1DrlfY657IpoGRkBge6rOKw82EqM_Xc5AK907nBAZ0zATrVdKYqnlrOryqgmljm8n5vT7qYXv8wNOxGCQ1zOuvs/tkzGVh7sZiZcqE3NsC0Gz_iEJA68lIl7/7" target="_blank"&gt;摩根大通在令人失望的第一季度交付后削减了估计&lt;/a&gt;。 Evercore ISI和瑞银的分析师已经&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/n