UamOZVrGkbe3alyCuOwS8t-79kd2TClBan1rbKNs0iSAq6mwTqaux6Lrq7ph3C7xo36OAmbUrFbUnf6cp7zHSVI73k1Q2Br8f2NfNa8deNH4cHgP7JeX8aFu0OwDsINGMEVi2E8HWMx3_r1tU-j7rBpjy2OtSfiHYt06fdLDoJfT_L6U76IDdQRIfRL5AiliVewCqDE5_xjkH0BSjWCcxDH7wCbU2G9hmGZKiFHDLRnVHWGiL58O4Coq1GKnNQVDYWJIpZenvAJ8sqIweK7DsQ/2-NB53UGDDdZqhwA5EjQyR1YNqzmKtD_/7" target="_blank"&gt;新关税&lt;/a&gt;，因为弗里德曼（Friedman）在与分析师的电话中讨论了RH的收益，似乎没有意识到特朗普（ &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/uZ7NKHE6C8CkYpYr1JTdDE1-umjCKn755ndVCC6pZuBFbqV-fr6Oah_pFZ3esmIrNx7Lro8GJwJ4KpPhzaD2RbVbcOhG9eMcER2g32_C5TKSr_7IuHOjlGSjg5vuCGOY7ojynCSf0mw7lUpwwpgLvOXgUvK6X7zvj4aqr2Mh9N-tDVx0HAXWc0AesqGVkhCgTUwzdIVxXrwnvq2rpBrmwwG6lxICvPA9QGUM2mqxRW3zce4rL5YXjDdj2x0z1j9cIPrSo0J-QXs8NjIVvTOFYTOErqoDJ8f2zoXBNbRzvLx1bkfWPKBLfSNuQLnNilduXHcDLgP0CAUdEjYVwqTMwpoHfcyVtpF1nnHDdeSXlS9H54VMR9N5P47Wo40/jDxOXl0SqczswjRxYup7jJZ4rSWwYw-j/7" target="_blank"&gt;Chaos Trump）释放的市场&lt;/a&gt;规模。他试图说服投资者， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/BdU0dpIj5aDlK7LSpZponZ8KHHXtW32MKFxIJNaRuK8cZQsII2x8dTSR-AivWNLwS5evcB3idooy11u5BtxSuLfKddTXISgRde999ECvZjEFChNtzUqptJCwDN5qSTdRBq-dE5cPdykbwWtfkTIDYUMSDvsUDlqbqNE2ySe65O7GK3d6TtjvEejUchqum7puLvDrfsYqQuOu9LPJ49EywZtN-uVxgdt3KEN3hkSjPlNC5cOhKIj5mJsnvU1opsChSOrOoZotqwLboh-6ULfXKPCmiIIuvGq1qaS4blSU2kXToVRAQqzpZUziAZcbY9s1iVOsgbnVQEBg1yIxpp4C_qkuME_cDwR9tDIbvyvi2XDYJe_jiYrQNn4-35k/vtXdruGYHNxA9EW0ue_3GadhBcPGpkBD/7" target="_blank"&gt;当他看着公司的股价时&lt;/a&gt;，零售商（经营修复硬件连锁店）是“位置良好的”。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;hr style="border-top-width: 1px; border-top-color: #CCC; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin: 10px;" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Ge