s-serif;"&gt;，美元已经消除了所有收益&lt;/strong&gt;。彭博（Bloomberg Dollar）的现货指数周四下降了1.5％，自10月中旬以来的最低水平结束。全球储备货币与美国债券收益率一起暴跌，并担心特朗普的贸易战争会减缓经济增长。贸易商寻求避风港，所有美元的100名同行（由日元和瑞士法郎）领导。美国阿蒙迪（Amundi）的固定收益和货币战略总监Paresh Upadhyaya说：“ &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/EZI677Sv7EhIdckEw0hmSyXC_6RzBwKDYnQaeFG8k0AyJaiKjt-Ua-472NpjwHmZCAc9mAtFHR-vWsG9zKweR1Cgn95gBA460zoJyWS-fq386q2MUXNqDNBonqIppHAVd83P4uhqJiRFJq4W9H6RJoLCae0mFAB4ocPv4UuExEUKZGn9hRgAGbpccAqAGUNYimFk6eEboqyOkR2nwO00DPuJZtYmhYlHbIaFnzVKI6Tmigqt48V2LWqVRHCF2p96_yV7mVIku84WotQa2HCGl2msHzNoWlY9KHhFWaTQaSBX1iEVWXhQH8SLGqcpdqsvTxx_9AROIbrOlUYfugrBG1SEivraZWVlKcECzIIKnUDCcH_EY6pARiVwJ-s/P1HnsXO8zT6JKUlufPithzJ7V-xAkYRA/7" target="_blank"&gt;美元的熊市已经到来，正在咆哮&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/cRfToNSa1qDqKCH6Uam1X0LybY256xiuxaS0UsTOeD-Ow1nW0cnIjIrDIOIZ-rTRYUvAny5a0zzWH7BzMdrfCt3eGNFAWvRirF1m4ujjEtU98E5nXeTiyMWLUNE2GP8rAgWTMzd-xEoaPvSA-3rrnON9uuPtvMZowFRTztEi4lRwuZilofG88z7cKwbmUlqP0Z7p2Rx_nyVYF83xkVkva2dD7basqZSAdw0fmpX4Pwta5yrYkcTlL-5O5jVvMFizdaGKF1jr2NWXOpoSzhbvZAitqeAadvoMCGGILfy0jCBdkJckkFvzOBuh1ktQQxFTwOwxamXgNSKsaO_f96iBo-_TgvMiML_72101mx9pI6ZZn_bUH6RY3EExgoA/H7XU9E7--1dP5yUnDy0XxiEOUPdiqdZw/7" target="_blank"&gt;。&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/AnY0rd8-xJKaDNs4qhrDZ0UrZYSBqWLLEn-N9eYWGQsA6KpdnMCh5uNpvWglghVzD1jqjKLxhqgfEeBGzxBB4ZOCdagpZYXNC9kqmffZJgTmPNQigUWkA56EUQ3VZruafv1yHwNL9e9-bVxiCD1zByAqcqgiNW7GuoIxhkZz3Z2fe_kJOjvKSbIHWmK8ofjTzHb59sjZcVehgYx_AZqGYA-SCiPGFrY7Whgpg1Z6DvkV1QtfCxtLaGlS47P7pqRkspFTwkV0IyHTZySxujA20B79Y-7Ye_VGumKMcWH2htL3djjBKGr42Dl5nvK2xkxd-NIXNrB8ptUd7soLBWVML4_RQSJNCU_Vm53IW1zm9wirYy_toYmd9ng0uZs/pdxDci3KJ_s_qjNP5cYfkzfQ0zVStv4U/7" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iIIDdau2_oIQ/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td